      COMMON /SOLVN/ NSLVRS                                              SUTERR........2300
      COMMON /VER/ VERNUM, VERNIN                                        SUTERR........2400
C                                                                        SUTERR........2500
C.....PARSE THE ERROR CODE                                               SUTERR........2600
