C           WHEN KMT=0, DECOMPOSE AND BACK-SUBSTITUTE,                   SUTRA........47600
C           WHEN KMT=2, BACK-SUBSTITUTE ONLY.                            SUTRA........47700
C        KPU=1 WHEN SOLVING FOR P,                                       SUTRA........47800
