C***TYPE      ALL (XERHLT-A)                                             SLAP........897900
C***KEYWORDS  ABORT PROGRAM EXECUTION, ERROR, XERROR                     SLAP........898000
C***AUTHOR  Jones, R. E., (SNLA)                                         SLAP........898100
C***DESCRIPTION                                                          SLAP........898200
C                                                                        SLAP........898300
C     Abstract                                                           SLAP........898400
